raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Hey... you still awake?
Player: Yeah? Duh, It's only 7 😂
Mabel: I can't sleep again 😔
Player: Oh you were trying to sleep now? 🤔
Mabel: I managed to finish unpacking but I'm super duper exhausted
Mabel: The dorm is quiet now so I thought it was a good chance to catch up on some sleep
Mabel: But now the silence is somehow super creepy 😣
Mabel: Thought: Am I the only one in this building?
- Aww, you scared?
	Player: Aww, you scared?
	Mabel: No!
	Mabel: Okay ...Maybe a little 🥺
- It's okay, I'll keep you company [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: It's okay, I'll keep you company
	Mabel: You're so sweet omg
	Mabel: You're the best boyfriend a girl could as for
	Player: 😇
Mabel: I heard people leaving their rooms
Mabel: Where are they going?
Player: I think everyone's gone out to town to party before orientation
Mabel: Is partying all people really do here??
Player: Well there aren't any classes yet sooo
Mabel: I see, yeah I guess that makes sense then
Mabel: But orientation still starts tomorrow
Player: Yeah 😅
Mabel: What do you think they're doing at these parties?
Mabel: I've never been to one but I've seen them in movies
- Probably just hanging out with friends [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: Probably just hanging out with friends
	Mabel: Oh okay
	Mabel: I don't think I'd want to go to a party
	Mabel: Why not a restaurant or cute cafe??
	Player: It's just a college culture thing I suppose
- Probably hanging out with their girlfriends [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: Probably hanging out with their girlfriends
	Mabel: Really??
	Mabel: Is that something you want to do with me? 🤔
	- Sure, why not?
		Player: Sure, why not?
		Player: It might be fun
		Mabel: Hmm I'm not 
		Mabel: But only if you promise to protect me 🥰
		Player: From what 😂 the scary dancers?
		Player: Sure!
		Mabel: Perfect hehe
		Mabel: You're so silly
		Mabel: img: mabel/11
	- Probably not [#trust]
		set Story.mabel_trust += 1
		Player: Probably not
		Player: I don't know if it would be a good idea haha
		Mabel: Yeah idk if I could enjoy something like that
		Mabel: I might end up acting uncomfortable and awkward
		Mabel: I'd ruin it 😭
		Player: Don't let it bother you 😆
		Player: We can always do other stuff!
- Probably hooking up [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Probably hooking up
	Mabel: Hooking.. up?
	Mabel: Oh you mean like 😬
	Player: Mhmm
	Mabel: Omg that's sooo bad... How can they just
	Mabel: Babe does that make any sense to you?
	- I don't get it either
		Player: I don't get it either
		Mabel: Right??
		Mabel: People need a relationship to do..
		Mabel: Y'knowww... 😅
		Player: You're so adorable 😊
	- Some people just like that kind of thing [#lust]
		set Story.mabel_desire += 1
		Player: Some people just like that kind of thing
		Mabel: I just don't understand it
		Mabel: That other girls like me?
		Mabel: Thought: Are they just going out and doing...
		Mabel: Ah nevermind 
		Mabel: It's almost like I'm on a different world
Mabel: I miss home already
Mabel: Or I'm homesick
Mabel: However you say it
Mabel: Don't you feel the same?
- A little [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: A little
	Mabel: I was hoping you'd say that
	Mabel: We can be all alone together at least! 🥹❤️
- Not really
	Player: Not really
	Mabel: Really? 
	Mabel: I guess you're stronger than me
	Mabel: Thought: I hope you let me rely on you
Player: Hey, it'll be fine
Player: Things are going to get easier
Mabel: You think so?
Player: I totally do
Mabel: Okay... I believe you 🥰
Mabel: I'll get some sleep now
Mabel: We have to be up early tomorrow
Mabel: Thanks for staying up with me
Player: Anytime 😊
Mabel: Thought: He's so sweet
Mabel: Goodnight! 🥰💤
Player: Night night 🌙
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
